Inputs of PT-JPL model are:
    Downwelling shortwave radiation (Rsd): AMATERASS (4km, 10min)
    Land surface temperature (LST): CEReS Yamamoto et al. (2km, hourly)
    Emissivity: MOD21A1 (1km, daily)
    NDVI: MOD31A2 (1km, 16days)
    Albedo: ERA5 (0.1째, hourly)
    Downwelling longwave radiation (Rld): ERA5 (0.1째, hourly)
    Dewpoint temperature (Td): ERA5 (0.1째, hourly)
    Air temperature (Ta): ERA5 (0.1째, hourly)